- follow shared 模块的标准 [shared.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/client/shared.mdc)
- logger 日志打印遵循 [logger.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/client/logger.mdc)
- client ui 视图层
    - styles 样式标准遵循 [styles.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/client/styles.mdc)
    - 新增 page 标准遵循 [pages.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/client/pages.mdc)
    - 下拉刷新的实现标准遵循 [pullDownRefresh.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/client/pullDownRefresh.mdc)
    - viewModel 的管理与使用标准遵循 [viewModel.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/client/viewModel.mdc) 
- client core 数据层
    - 与 server app 交互的 api 标准遵循 [api.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/client/api.mdc)
